.el .ds Aq '
.TH DELPHI-TYPO 1  "delphitools-cli 0.1.0" "delphitools manual"
.SH NAME
typo \- Convert between typographic units (pt, px, mm, em, rem, pc, in, cm)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBtypo\fR [\fB\-\-base\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIVALUE\fR> [\fITARGETS\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Convert between typographic units (pt, px, mm, em, rem, pc, in, cm)
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-base\fR \fI<BASE>\fR [default: 16]
Base font size in px (for em/rem conversions)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fIVALUE\fR>
Value with unit, e.g. "12pt"
.TP
[\fITARGETS\fR]
Target unit(s) (e.g. px,mm,pc). Shows all if omitted
